{
  "stem": "12491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But if I remember correctly, maybe 50 of them were still alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He brought them back into the Schindler's camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He set them up in an empty factory building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Schindler and him fed them all the goodies which the Germans couldn't even get, milk, cereals, whatever, and brought, to the best of my knowledge, all of them back to health.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were pretty much half dead when they arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do you know that it happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw them coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I talked to them after they were placed in the empty factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I talked to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eventually, they were incorporated into the working force, but for a very short time because it was almost liberation time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, about three days before the actual capitulation of Germany, Schindler called on the electrical department to take large stickers from his office, hang them in the factory, and from his beautiful Blaupunkt stereo-- maybe not stereo, but radio-- beam BBC News from England onto the factory so that we would be aware of what is going on.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS was still in power.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he, risking, in my opinion, his life, allowed this to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And wires were wheeled out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when our guy was involved in it, to a small degree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Speakers were placed, and we heard from London, from BBC-- in Polish, because we didn't speak English-- in Polish the news about German capitulation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The day before the Germans actually capitulated, with the SS still being in the camp, Schindler had what is known now as his famous speech.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The speech was a little bit different than is being publicized now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't have it written down anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
